README.MXE

Tools for forcing files.

See sample shell scripts (sample/).



==== Fortran program (src/) ====

remap_ctl.F90
    Make remapping table for interpolation.

interpolate_ctl.F90
    Interpolate forcing files to MRI.COM grid
      based on a remapping table.
    Only for scalar data at T-Grid.


==== Fortran module ====

force_data.F90
    module to read forcing files
